name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $identifier
desc: Returns: An external identifier for this statement such as an IRI.

name: $addidentifier
desc: An external identifier for this statement such as an IRI.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: An external identifier for this statement such as an IRI.

name: $status
desc: Returns: A code representing the patient or other source's judgment about the state of the device used that this statement is about.  Generally this will be active or completed.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A code representing the patient or other source's judgment about the state of the device used that this statement is about.  Generally this will be active or completed.

name: $subject
desc: Returns: The patient who used the device.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The patient who used the device.

name: $whenUsed
desc: Returns: The time period over which the device was used.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The time period over which the device was used.

name: $recordedOn
desc: Returns: The time at which the statement was made/recorded.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The time at which the statement was made/recorded.

name: $source
desc: Returns: Who reported the device was being used by the patient.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Who reported the device was being used by the patient.

name: $device
desc: Returns: The details of the device used.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The details of the device used.

name: $indication
desc: Returns: Reason or justification for the use of the device.

name: $addindication
desc: Reason or justification for the use of the device.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Reason or justification for the use of the device.

name: $bodySite
desc: Returns: Indicates the site on the subject's body where the device was used ( i.e. the target site).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates the site on the subject's body where the device was used ( i.e. the target site).

name: $note
desc: Returns: Details about the device statement that were not represented at all or sufficiently in one of the attributes provided in a class. These may include for example a comment, an instruction, or a note associated with the statement.

name: $addnote
desc: Details about the device statement that were not represented at all or sufficiently in one of the attributes provided in a class. These may include for example a comment, an instruction, or a note associated with the statement.

lvardefs.desc: Details about the device statement that were not represented at all or sufficiently in one of the attributes provided in a class. These may include for example a comment, an instruction, or a note associated with the statement.
